OL,3,CFrank Lampard signs new contract with
OL,4,CCoventry City until 2029
OL,6,FCoventry City have announced that Head
OL,7,FCoach Frank Lampard has signed a new
OL,8,Fcontract with the club until 2029.
OL,10,FThe 48-year-old has enjoyed a
OL,11,Fsuccessful period since taking charge
OL,12,Fback in November 2024.
OL,14,FLampard guided the club to the Sky Bet
OL,15,FChampionship title last term after
OL,16,Ftaking the team from 17th position in
OL,17,Fthe league to the play offs in his
OL,18,Ffirst season. In his second season in
OL,19,Fcharge, Coventry were promoted to the
OL,20,FPremier League for the first time in
OL,21,F25 years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
