OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782908305
OL,3,CFrank Lampard signs new contract with
OL,4,CCoventry City until 2029
OL,6,FThe former England midfielder has
OL,7,Ftaken charge of 82 matches in total,
OL,8,Fwinning 45 of them.
OL,10,FPromotion was celebrated by nearly
OL,11,F250,000 people in the city, as the
OL,12,Fteam paraded around the the streets on
OL,13,Fan open top bus.
OL,15,FLampard said: "I'm delighted to have
OL,16,Fsigned a new contract, it's a real
OL,17,Fhonour to represent this club.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782908305
OL,3,CFrank Lampard signs new contract with
OL,4,CCoventry City until 2029
OL,6,F"After the incredible work of
OL,7,Feverybody to get promoted and win the
OL,8,FChampionship, it was important to
OL,9,Fenjoy the moment, and we certainly did
OL,10,Fas a city.
OL,12,F"Our job then as staff, and for the
OL,13,Fplayers of course, is to firstly
OL,14,Frecharge but also focus on what we
OL,15,Fwant to do and what we need to for
OL,16,Fnext season. There's a lot of work to
OL,17,Fdo on and off the pitch as a football
OL,18,Fclub, so those things have been on
OL,19,Fgoing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782908305
OL,3,CFrank Lampard signs new contract with
OL,4,CCoventry City until 2029
OL,6,F"I'm looking forward to getting back
OL,7,Fwith the players, to see them all and
OL,8,Fget ready for the new season.
OL,10,F"I'd like to thank everyone at the
OL,11,Ffootball club. The fans first and
OL,12,Fforemost for how they've supported the
OL,13,Fteam, myself and my staff in allowing
OL,14,Fus to get to where we've got to. The
OL,15,Fspirit and togetherness we created
OL,16,Flast year was something great to be
OL,17,Fpart of and now we want to continue it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
