CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782908305
OL,3,CFrank Lampard signs new contract with
OL,4,CCoventry City until 2029
OL,6,F"Thank you to Doug King as well for
OL,7,Fgiving me the opportunity to come to
OL,8,Fthis football club and for his support
OL,9,Fof us. We work together and we know
OL,10,Fthere's a lot to do but we're going to
OL,11,Fgive it everything."
OL,13,FOwner and Executive Chairman Doug King
OL,14,Fadded: "I am absolutely delighted that
OL,15,FFrank and his team have "signed the
OL,16,Fcontract," so to speak.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]vD@HOUwD@YOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
