PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1782908305
OL,3,CFrank Lampard signs new contract with
OL,4,CCoventry City until 2029
OL,6,F"Since arriving in November 2024, our
OL,7,Fclub has been on a huge upward
OL,8,Ftrajectory under his leadership and it
OL,9,Fis absolutely fitting after
OL,10,FChampionship glory last season that he
OL,11,Fleads us into our first Premier League
OL,12,Fseason for a generation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@YO]
